      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 74.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 74.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>民不畏死，奈何以死懼之？若使民常畏死，而為奇者，吾得執而殺之，孰敢？</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The people do not fear death; to what purpose is it to (try to) frighten them with death? If the people were always in awe of death, and I could always seize those who do wrong, and put them to death, who would dare to do wrong?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-074__align-002">
